koohiiStory1: Your address should be displayed on your house and mailbox.
koohiiStory2: For the primitive: This is a hi-tech Japanese mailbox, it automatically lights up in the evening, and has a biometric fingerprint scanner. --- Each house´s address, even if it´s hard to see in the evening, is like its own unique fingerprint.
kunYomi: あ.てる、-あて、-づつ、あたか.も
words:
宛(あて): addressed to
宛てる(あてる): to address
宛名(あてな): address, direction
